   "question": "Where does Restoration Druid Phase 2 BiS come from?",
   "answer": "From the gear worn by 310 top-ranked Restoration Druid healing parses on Warcraft Logs during Phase 2 (Serpentshrine Cavern and Tempest Keep), aggregated per slot — what high parsers actually equip, not a spreadsheet ideal."
