  {
   "question": "What are the highest-consensus Restoration Druid items in Phase 2?",
   "answer": "Idol of the Emerald Queen (67%), Grove-Bands of Remulos (65%), Nordrassil Life-Mantle (55%). When an item sits above ~70% among top parsers, treat it as the priority drop to chase."
  },
  {
   "question": "Should I follow this list exactly for Phase 2?",
